{"tid":421920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐盟指加泰公投違反西班牙憲法","createTime":"2017-10-02T15:34:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T05:12:21.000Z","uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0ebb462d2229fd4adb97aecf91a3ab52f3982ec4","tid":421920,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:34:14.000Z","msg":"歐盟委員會確認加泰隆尼亞獨立公投違反西班牙憲法，並稱週日事故屬西班牙內部事務，歐盟不會插手干預，並指必須捍衛西班牙法治云云。<br />\n若加泰依西班牙憲法舉辦公投，通過後即自動脫離歐盟。撇除法律層面，歐盟更重視團結和穩定，而非分化與離散。<br />\n委員會寄望西班牙及加泰政府能透過對話化解分歧，並指暴力不能解決問題，相信西班牙首相會透過合法合憲和尊重人權的手法解決。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/momongzai/posts/10155603661853346\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmomongzai%2Fposts%2F10155603661853346&d=%2BdsC6E34029Fg2a%2B2CxznW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=5a38f8ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/momongzai/posts/10155603661853346</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/catalan-independence-referendum-not-legal-spanish-constitution-european-commission-juncker-spain-law-a7978386.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fcatalan-independence-referendum-not-legal-spanish-constitution-european-commission-juncker-spain-law-a7978386.html&d=%2BdsC6E34029Fg2a%2B2CxznW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=39536fd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/catalan-independence-referendum-not-legal-spanish-constitution-european-commission-juncker-spain-law-a7978386.html</a>"},{"pid":"7f0c5d04dc80dcaf039394f6361cfd8317b8c896","tid":421920,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:36:50.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;This is an internal matter for Spain that has to be dealt with in line with the constitutional order of Spain,&rdquo; a spokesperson said.<br />\n<br />\n今次係西班牙內部事務，要依照西班牙憲法依法解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIn what appeared to be a reference to police brutality against voters, a statement said &ldquo;violence can never be an instrument in politics&rdquo;, adding: &ldquo;We trust the leadership of Prime Minister Mariano Rajoy to manage this difficult process in full respect of the Spanish constitution and of the fundamental rights of citizens enshrined therein.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n連condemn暴力都無，只係話相信rajoy可以捍衛法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔怪得連俄佬都笑班垃圾，平時指指點點，依家就咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9edcf21c828068c31676e2aebf634959854e84cb","tid":421920,"uid":27151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:39:48.000Z","msg":"歐盟真係好撚偽善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時滿口仁義道德，一牽涉到自身利益就選擇性失明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eeb25ff155324412062bb2e841d238a6b4d2eb7","tid":421920,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T01:18:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46c849f6a313ad9769dba074844032851e86b659","tid":421920,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T01:25:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>歐盟真係好撚偽善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時滿口仁義道德，一牽涉到自身利益就選擇性失明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一班左膠集合體. <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93bbc9477a9090ad54023ffd61b45434eb6bc863","tid":421920,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T01:46:58.000Z","msg":"有時唔好怪人悲觀主義"},{"pid":"9238978ae613eab4bf5d81c3cf7275f399514e69","tid":421920,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T04:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":